_sText: The download file was wrong, but now its fixed. Only one member got to download the wrong file. My apologizes. So, this is my first prefab ever, its just a simple tower, with 2 floors. It has got dev textures on it, so if you want to re-texture it, just replace the textures; dev/dev_measuregeneric01 dev/dev_blendmeasure To install this prefab, put the .vmf from the extracted file into; C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\UserName\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs And when you choose the entity tool and set the subtool as prefabs, you will find the tower by typing in ''omena'' full name is omena_towerprefab_fix. There are credits inside the tower for me, you can delete it if you want, or leave it if you're so kind. =) *Note that when you have downloaded the prefab, and put it in your map, the wall/ground/skybox are not included. Enjoy it, Omena,
